item.title: My server is down?
item.dc:creator: @Harleyscape_owner Harleyscape owner
item.description:
@Harleyscape_owner wrote:

ok first yes “0.0.0.0:43594” that is normal well if you want other’s to join, go to www.moparisthebest.com/serverstatus.php and register and put your no-ip there and for port put 43594, and if that does not work go to www.ipchicken.com and there they will tell you your ip which will be number’s so then go back to www.moparisthebest.com/serverstatus.php and then redo your registration and for the ip put the numbers that www.ipchicken.com gave you, if you still have trouble pm me or post here thanks hope this helps.

~Harleyscape owner
